title: 1922–23 Tranmere Rovers F.C. season
text: <a href="Tranmere%20Rovers%20F.C.">Tranmere Rovers F.C.</a> played the 1922–23 season in the <a href="Football%20League%20Third%20Division%20North">Football League Third Division North</a>. It was their second season of league <a href="Association%20football">football</a>, and they finished 16th of 20. They reached the Fourth Qualifying Round of the <a href="FA%20Cup">FA Cup</a>.
